Package: shinyDownload
Title: Shiny module that allows tables, plots and reports to be downloaded
    in Shiny
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Keith", "Newman", , "knewma@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shiny module designed to allow plots and data frames to be
    downloaded and reports to be compiled from an RMarkdown template and
    then downloaded.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.0.1)
Imports:
    cli,
    jsonlite,
    lifecycle,
    rmarkdown,
    shiny (>= 1.5.0),
    yaml,
    zip
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Collate:
    'downloadGGPlot.R'
    'downloadReport.R'
    'downloadTable.R'
    'shinyDownloadExample.R'
